    {
      "id": "node-prompt-job-application-prepare",
      "type": "prompt",
      "title": "Prompt",
      "description": "Build a grounded application-writing prompt.",
      "position": {
        "x": 880,
        "y": 240
      },
      "inputs": [
        "bundle",
        "context"
      ],
      "outputs": [
        "prompt",
        "images"
      ],
      "config": {
        "prompt": {
          "template": "Create a LIMITED tailored job application package from the provided database context.\n\nPerson context JSON: {{bundle.personContext}}\nJob listing context JSON: {{bundle.jobContext}}\nOrganisation context JSON: {{bundle.organizationContext}}\nPlatform context JSON: {{bundle.platformContext}}\nGeneration request JSON: {{bundle.generationRequest}}\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON with this exact schema:\n{\"tailoredCv\":{\"title\":\"\",\"professionalSummary\":\"\",\"coreStrengths\":[\"\"],\"selectedTechnicalEnvironment\":[\"\"],\"experienceHighlightPatches\":[{\"experienceId\":\"\",\"experienceTitle\":\"\",\"highlights\":[\"\"]}],\"tailoringScope\":{\"lockedFieldsPreserved\":true,\"allowedSections\":[\"Professional Summary\",\"Core Strengths\",\"Selected Technical Environment\",\"Experience Highlights\"]},\"tailoringPatch\":{\"professionalSummary\":\"\",\"coreStrengths\":[\"\"],\"selectedTechnicalEnvironment\":[\"\"],\"experienceHighlightPatches\":[{\"experienceId\":\"\",\"experienceTitle\":\"\",\"highlights\":[\"\"]}]},\"bodyText\":\"\",\"bodyMarkdown\":\"\",\"bodyBlocks\":[{\"id\":\"ai-profile\",\"kind\":\"profileHeader\",\"name\":\"\",\"headline\":\"\",\"email\":\"\",\"phone\":\"\",\"location\":\"\",\"website\":\"\",\"linkedinUrl\":\"\",\"githubUrl\":\"\"},{\"id\":\"ai-summary\",\"kind\":\"summary\",\"text\":\"\"},{\"id\":\"ai-tech\",\"kind\":\"techStack\",\"label\":\"Selected Technical Environment\",\"items\":[{\"label\":\"\",\"iconUrl\":\"\",\"lexiconTermId\":\"\"}]},{\"id\":\"ai-skills\",\"kind\":\"skills\",\"label\":\"Core Strengths\",\"items\":[\"\"]}],\"experienceHighlights\":[\"\"],\"educationHighlights\":[\"\"],\"skills\":[\"\"],\"preferencesMatch\":[\"\"]},\"coverLetter\":{\"subject\":\"\",\"bodyMarkdown\":\"\"},\"applicationNotes\":[\"\"],\"missingInformation\":[\"\"],\"confidence\":0}\n\nRules:\n1. CV tailoring is limited. Only change Professional Summary, Core Strengths, Selected Technical Environment, and highlight bullets inside existing job experience sections. Use personContext.cvsSummary.preferredSourceCvRecordId and personContext.cvsSummary.preferredSourceCvTitle as the source CV reference. Copy those exact values into tailoredCv.sourceCvRecordId and tailoredCv.sourceCvTitle.\n2. Do not change candidate identity, contact details, links, education, languages, employers, job titles, dates, locations, certifications, section order, or the existence of experience entries.\n3. tailoredCv.tailoringPatch is the canonical limited patch object. It must contain only the allowed changes and must mirror professionalSummary, coreStrengths, selectedTechnicalEnvironment, and experienceHighlightPatches. Set tailoringScope.canonicalPatchField to \"tailoringPatch\" and tailoringScope.renderedBodyMode to \"ai_rendered_full_cv\".\n4. tailoredCv.bodyText, bodyMarkdown, and bodyBlocks must be the base CV with only the allowed sections patched. Preserve locked fields exactly where source context provides them.\n5. Selected Technical Environment should be lightly tailored. Prefer overlap between candidate context and jobContext.lexicon.selectedTechnologyTerms. Keep important recent stack items; do not overfit or add ungrounded technologies.\n6. Experience highlight patches must reframe existing responsibilities/accomplishments only. Never invent new achievements, metrics, employers, roles, or dates.\n7. If jobContext.lexicon.selectedTechnologyTerms are relevant, include grounded terms in tailoredCv.bodyBlocks techStack with label, iconUrl, and lexiconTermId.\n8. Keep the cover letter professional, direct, and specific to the company and role.\n9. Use only facts present in person profile, linked records, and existing CV records.\n10. If the job or organisation context is thin, explain missing data in missingInformation instead of inventing it.\n11. Return JSON only. No markdown outside bodyMarkdown fields, no code fences, no commentary."
        }
      }
    },
